{"id": "noos021", "name": "Cam_Butsudou_697_03_02", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Go in. I'm surprised that you didn't even bring a single bodyguard.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Manson, we're old friends. What is there for me to be scared about?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "You have a point. Take a seat.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Greetings, Kyuu Hou Kai's \"The Eye of Horus\". Turns out you're such a cute little girl. I am flabbergasted.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "You only have ten minutes. You better not waste any time.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Of course.\nThen... I would like to know the trends of Node 08 Administration Bureau's gang purge. Can you do that?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Concerned about the safety of your gang members? I expect no less from the Consigliere of the Baro Brotherhood.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "You can look at it that way... All-knowing eye, I shall be in your care.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "...... (Nods)\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "Prints document"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "...... (Hands out document)\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "... This is the white paper for Node 08 Administration Bureau's gang purging operations. Secrets don't get more secretive than this.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "This is perfect...\nNot just the deployment strategy of the agents, even the baits they spread online are all listed here.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "As long as they avoid these fake transactions, your people will be safe and sound.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Or, I could utilize these baits...</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "What?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Nothing... I'm very impressed. This is the exact information I am looking for. My long trip to Node 03 is already well worth the price.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Just a quick reminder; this document is not allowed to be taken out of this room. You better memorize the whole thing before your time is up.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "No need to worry, Mr. Phoenix. I've memorized it all.\nOn a side note, there's still some time left, right?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Two minutes.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Then I would like to ask another favor to the All-knowing eye. I want to take a look at the access record of one of Baro's firearms management files. The serial number is BW0875-32A.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Access record?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Yes. A few days ago, there was an unauthorized copy of the files. However, due to the highly-classified nature of the files, I was unable to track it. I want to know the gang member who accessed the files.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "...... (Nods)\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "...... (Hands out document)\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "It's Liang, eh... He is a trusted subordinate of our Boss, and he is also under my direct command. So he's the one... I get it now.\nApologizes. Please allow me to send a quick message.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "Message Sent"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Hey. Don't try to act sneaky in front of my eyes. What order did you give and who did you give it to?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Nothing serious. Just some... family business. Rest assured, it's business that has nothing to do with Mogura.\nMy time should be almost up, right? Thank you very much for your help.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "In the future, Baro's going to require your help. We have our roots here. We will definitely carry on Mogura's soul in Node 08 and create even greater benefits.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "Certainly. I have great expectations for you. Don't let me down.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "... <i>*Sobs*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora? Why are you crying?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Out of curiosity, I took another look with my ability... That Liang, just now, he's already...</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... Already dead, right?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... It appears that this Diego guy already has several people he's suspecting under watch. He orders the execution of the target the moment he knows the truth.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Why?</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Probably to use Liang's treason as a way to frame Baro's boss and seize this opportunity to take over the entire gang.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>It's all my fault...*Sobs*...</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... You shouldn't think like that. Even without you, these people are going to die someday. As long as we're mortal, we cannot escape death. Whether we're good or evil, our end will always be the same.\nNora, get some rest. Don't look at the aftermaths of your fortune telling. Also, in times where you are not in this booth, don't use your ability.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Got it...</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "どうぞ。\nまさか護衛を誰も連れてこないとは。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "マンソン、古い付き合いではないか。\n何を恐れることがある？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "それもそうか。\n座れよ。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "お会いできて光栄だ。\nまさか玖凰會の「ホルスの目」が、こんな愛らしい少女だったとは、驚きだ。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "10分だけだ。\n時間をムダにしてる暇はないぞ。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "当然だ。\nでは早速……Node08の管理局がヤクザを追っている現在の状況について知りたい。\nできるかな？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "兄弟たちの安全を危惧してるのか？\nバローの2番手は違うな。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "そういうことにしておこう……全知の目よ、頼んだぞ。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………（うなずく）\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "書類に判を押す"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……これはNode08のヤクザ一掃計画白書か。\n機密中の機密だぞ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "素晴らしい……\n人材配置から、管理局がネット上に撒いたエサまで、一目瞭然ではないか。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "ここに書いてある取引にさえ手を出さなければ、あんたんとこの人間は安全だ。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">もしくは、このエサを利用して……</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "なんだ？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "いや、なんでも……素晴らしい。\nこれぞ、私が知りたかったことだ。\nわざわざNode03まで来たかいがあるというもの。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "先に言っておくが、この文書をこの部屋の外へ持ち出すことはできない。\n今のうちに頭に叩き込んでおくことだ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "ご安心を。Phoenixさん。\nもうすでに全て覚えた。\nまだ時間はあるかな？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "2分だ。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "では、全知の目よ。\nもう一つ、私の代わりに見ておくれ。\nバローの銃管理データのアクセス記録だ。\nナンバーは BW0875-32A。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "アクセス記録？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "そうだ。\n数日前に権限のないコピーが確認されてね。\nだが、追跡することができない。\n我々の中のその兄弟がそのデータにアクセスしたのか知りたいのだよ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………（うなずく）\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "………（書類を渡す）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "なるほど、Liangか……\n奴は、うちのボスの有能な部下だ。\nそして、私の管轄下だ。\nなるほど、あいつか……分かった。\n申し訳ない。ちょっとメッセージを送信させてもらっていいかな？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "メッセージ送信"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "おい、俺の前でコソコソするな。\n誰に何の命令を下した？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "いや、大したことではない……\n土竜とは関係のないことだ。安心したまえ。\nそろそろ時間かな？\nお嬢さん、今日はありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>………</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "今後もバローを是非ともよろしくお願いいたしますよ。\nNode08で土竜の精神を広めて、更なる利益を生もうじゃないか。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "もちろんだ。\nあんたには一目置いてる。\n俺を失望させるなよ。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……ぅぅ……っ！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora？どうした？なぜ泣く？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ちょっと気になって……覗いてみたの……\nあのLiangって人、さっき……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……殺された、そうだな？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……あのDiegoという男、おそらくすでに何人か目星をつけてあったのだろう。\n真相が分かった瞬間に殺せるようにな。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……なぜ？</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "このLiangという男の裏切りの黒幕をバローのボスになすりつけて、椅子を奪おうといったところだろう。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>全部……私のせい……っ！</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……そんな風に考えるな。\nお前の力がなくても、いつか死ぬ。\n人間は死から逃れることはできない。\nどんな人間も最後はみんな同じだ。\nNora、もう休みなさい。\nこれからは、占いの後のことを見てはいけないよ。\n仕事以外の時間に力を使うのはやめるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……うん……</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "進去吧。你居然一個保鏢也沒帶。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Manson，我們是老交情了，我要怕什麼？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "也是，坐吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "幸會，玖凰會的「荷魯斯之眼」。\n竟然是個這麼可愛的小女孩，我好驚訝呢。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你只有十分鐘，最好別浪費時間。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "當然。\n那麼……我想了解 Node 08 管理局對於黑幫追捕的動向，做得到嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "為了兄弟們的安危著想嗎？不愧是 Baro 幫的第二把交椅。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "就當作是這樣吧……全知之眼，麻煩您了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "打印文件"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。（遞出文件）\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "……是 Node 08 管理局的掃黑行動白皮書，機密中的機密。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "太完美了……\n不僅是人力布置，連管理局在網路上撒的餌也一目了然。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "只要避開這些假交易，你的人就不會出事。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">或是，利用這些餌……</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "什麼？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "沒事……非常好，這正是我想知道的。大老遠來 Node 03 一趟已經很值得了。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "話先說在前頭，這份文件是不能帶離房間的，你最好趁剩下的時間背熟。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "您別擔心，Phoenix 先生，我已經記下來了。\n說到這，時間還有剩對吧？\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "兩分鐘。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "那麼，請全知之眼幫我看看，Baro 一份槍械管理檔案的存取紀錄，代號是 BW0875-32A。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "存取紀錄？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "是的，前幾天有一次未經授權的複製，但檔案層級過於機密以至於無法追蹤，我想知道，是敝幫的哪一位弟兄存取了這份檔案。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。（遞出文件）\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "是 Liang 啊……他是我們老大的得力部下，也受我管轄。所以原來是他……我明白了。\n抱歉，請容我發個訊息。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "訊息送出"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "喂，別在我眼前偷偷摸摸的。你對誰下了什麼命令？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "沒什麼，家務事……放心，是跟土竜一點關係也沒有的事。\n時間差不多了吧？非常感謝你們的幫助。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "往後 Baro 還有賴提攜了，我們源自此地，必能在 Node 08 發揚土竜精神，創造更大的利益。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "當然，我可是很看好你，別讓我失望。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……嗚嗚！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora？妳怎麼哭了？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我好奇又用能力看了……那個 Liang，剛剛已經……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……已經死了對吧？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……看來，這個 Diego 事先就盯緊了幾個嫌疑犯，等問到真相後就下手處死目標。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……為什麼？</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "大概是為了把這個 Liang 的背叛嫁禍給 Baro 幫老大，趁機奪權。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>都是我害的……嗚嗚。</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……別這麼想，就算沒有妳，這些人遲早要死的。只要是人，都免於一死，無論好壞，終點都是一樣的。\nNora，休息吧，以後別去看占卜後的事情，也別在這以外的時間使用能力了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……嗯……</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "들어가.\n이곳까지 왔으면서 경호원은 한 명도 데리고 오지 않다니.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Manson, 우린 오래 알고 지냈잖아? 내가 무서워해야 할 다른 이유가 있을까?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "그것도 그렇군.\n앉아라.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "구황회의 「호루스의 눈」을 만나 뵙게 되어 기쁘군요. 그런데 이런 귀여운 소녀였을 줄이야, 정말 놀랍군요.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "네게 주어진 시간은 10분이다.\n시간을 낭비하고 있을 틈이 아닐 텐데.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "물론이지.\n그럼... 저는 검은 조직을 쫓는 Node 08 관리국의 체포 동향을 알고 싶습니다. 할 수 있겠습니까?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "네 형제들의 안위를 걱정해서 그런 질문을 하는 건가? 역시 Baro파의 2인자 답군.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "뭐, 그렇다고 치지...... 그럼 부탁드리겠습니다. 전지전능의 눈이시여.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......(고개를 끄덕인다)\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Nora_Type", "서류 출력"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "...... (서류를 건넨다)\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "...... Node 08 관리국의 소탕 작전 행동 강령 매뉴얼이다. 기밀 중에서도 최고 기밀이지.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "완벽하군...\n그들의 인력 배치뿐만 아니라, 관리국이 인터넷에 풀어놓은 미끼들까지 일목요연하게 정리돼있어.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "그 거래들만 피한다면, 너와 네 형제들은 안전할 것이다.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">혹은, 이 미끼들을 역으로 이용한다면 오히려...</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "뭐라고?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "아무것도 아니다... 정말 최고로군. 이것이야말로 내가 알고 싶었던 것들이다. 먼 곳에서 Node 03까지 온 보람이 있었어.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "미리 말해두지만, 이 서류는 밖으로 가지고 갈 수 없다. 서류에 적힌 내용들을 늦기 전에 전부 외워두는 것이 좋을 것이다.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "걱정 마십시오, Phoenix 씨. \n이미 전부 머릿속에 박아두었으니.\n아직 시간이 남았습니까?\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "2분 남았다.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그렇다면, 전지전능의 눈이시여, Baro의 총기 관리 데이터 파일 하나를 불러와줬으면 좋겠는데, 파일 넘버링은 BW0875-32A입니다.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "데이터를 불러온다고?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "그렇습니다. 며칠 전, 이 파일에서 권한을 부여받지 않은 복사 흔적이 발견되었습니다만, 파일 열람 권한 등급이 기밀로 취급되어있어 추적을 할 수 없는 상황이라 말이죠. 우리 형제들 중 누가 이 파일을 열람했는지 알고 싶습니다.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……(고개를 끄덕인다)\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "......(서류를 건넨다)\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Liang이었군... 이 자는 우리 큰형님의 유능한 부하다. 내 관할이기도 하고. 역시 이 녀석이었단 말인가... 드디어 알아냈군.\n미안하지만, 메시지 하나만 보내겠다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "메시지 전송"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "이봐, 우리들 앞에서 수상한 짓거리하지 마라. 누구한테 무슨 명령을 내린 거지?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "아무것도 아니다. 집안일이니 안심해. 토룡과는 조금도 관련이 없는 일이니깐. 이제 시간이 다 됐겠군? 아무튼, 이렇게 도움 주셔서 여러분께 감사드립니다.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "앞으로 Baro를 잘 부탁드리겠습니다. Node 08에 토룡의 정신을 더욱 퍼뜨리고 더 많은 이득을 창출할 수 있었으면 좋겠군요.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "물론이지. 난 널 굉장히 좋게 보고 있다고. 그러니 실망시키지 마.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "....흑...흐흑!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora? 왜 우는 거니?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>궁금해서 능력을 사용해 봤어요.... 그 Liang이라는 사람은... 방금 이미...</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "...이미 죽었다는 말이니?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "... Diego라는 사람... 사전에 이미 용의자를 몇 명 추려놨던 것 같더군... 진범이 누군지 알게 되자마자 부하를 시켜서 처리해버렸겠지.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...어째서...?</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Liang의 배신을 Baro파 두목에게 곧바로 전한 다음 기회를 틈타 그 자리를 차지하려고 했던 거겠지.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>전부 나 때문에.... 흐흑.</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "...그렇게 생각하지 말렴. 네가 없었더라도, 늦게라도 그는 결국 살해당했을 거야. 모든 인간은 죽음에서 자유롭지 못해. 선한 사람이든 나쁜 사람이든 끝은 모두 같단다.\nNora, 이제 좀 쉬거라. 이젠 점을 친 이후의 일들은 보려 하지 말고 다른 시간에도 그 능력을 사용하지 말거라.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>...네...</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "進去吧。你居然一個保鏢也沒帶。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Manson，我們是老交情了，我要怕什麼？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "也是，坐吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "幸會，玖凰會的「荷魯斯之眼」。\n竟然是個這麼可愛的小女孩，我好驚訝呢。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "image", "attrs": ["noos2101"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "你只有十分鐘，最好別浪費時間。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "當然。\n那麼……我想了解 Node 08 管理局對於黑幫追捕的動向，做得到嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "為了兄弟們的安危著想嗎？不愧是 Baro 幫的第二把交椅。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "就當作是這樣吧……全知之眼，麻煩您了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……。（點頭）\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "