偷摸摸的。你對誰下了什麼命令？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "沒什麼，家務事……放心，是跟土竜一點關係也沒有的事。\n時間差不多了吧？非常感謝你們的幫助。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……。</i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "往後 Baro 還有賴提攜了，我們源自此地，必能在 Node 08 發揚土竜精神，創造更大的利益。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "當然，我可是很看好你，別讓我失望。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Nora"], "content": "……嗚嗚！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "Nora？妳怎麼哭了？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>我好奇又用能力看了……那個 Liang，剛剛已經……</i>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……已經死了對吧？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……看來，這個 Diego 事先就盯緊了幾個嫌疑犯，等問到真相後就下手處死目標。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……為什麼？</i>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "大概是為了把這個 Liang 的背叛嫁禍給 Baro 幫老大，趁機奪權。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>都是我害的……嗚嗚。</i>\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Phoenix"], "content": "……別這麼想，就算沒有妳，這些人遲早要死的。只要是人，都免於一死，無論好壞，終點都是一樣的。\nNora，休息吧，以後別去看占卜後的事情，也別在這以外的時間使用能力了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……嗯……</i>\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Butsudou"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["DoorButsudou", "开门"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "进去吧。你居然一个保镖也没带。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Diego"], "content": "Manson，我们是老交情了，我要怕什么？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Lam"], "content": "也是，坐吧。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "